---
title: Turkey Spring Roll-Inspired Bowls with Crispy Shallots
description: Everyone's favourite appetizer can make a delicious dinner with a little creativity! This de-constructed spring roll bowl is packed with soft, fluffy jasmine rice; crispy shallots; savoury, sticky turkey and crunchy slaw. Top it all with a drizzle of plum sauce.
